<plot>Set in the Mississippi Delta, "Revisited" is the story of Ferrel Pittman, who upon his father Able's return home, is forced to confront their two severed pasts. When Able's memories of the 1927 flood begin to resurface, Ferrel must come to terms with his father's role in the death of a Mississippi River levee worker killed during the flood.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?462169</url></doc>
